wpt.desc: Memorial to Life by Team JNLE4, Traditional Cache (1/1.5)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Memorial to Life
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: The cache is log only cache, so bring a pen. It should be an easy find, this cache is about location and not about difficulty. Have fun!
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
You have probably noticed this location as you have driven past on Ohio SR315. I knew I needed to place a cache here and it took a bit. The cache has been placed with permission from the owners of the memorial. As always be respectful of the location and take some time and look around.
*** Congratulations to JCPJcrew on the FTF! ***

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text:
Took me a few minutes to find it, but I got my first OH cache while on a business trip from PA. Thanks for bringing me to the spot.
Log is very wet. I laid it out for a few minutes but it needs more.
